Text.Value: Just like the rest of your kind, aren't you?
You shouldn't be stealing, you filthy little vermin.
There's no time to waste - seize what you can carry!

EditorData.NodeContext: Pretty excited by the food revolution

Text.Value: Good - your traitorous clodhoppers stand in the way of justice!
I'm with you - food should be shared and enjoyed, not hidden away.
Do what you want - I don't care.
I'll stay out of your way.
But in the dead of night, when sleep overcomes your stinking flesh pile, our bellies will be filled!

EditorData.NodeContext: Annoyed but trying to leave with dignity; a rodent threat

Text.Value: Oh yes. And you should definitely rise and overthrow those oppressors while you're at it.
I don't want you and your family to starve - take what you need.
How is any of this yours?
Halt, oppressor! I am reclaiming the victuals in this basement for the good of ratkind!

EditorData.NodeContext: Combative - believes they're standing up for what's right

Text.Value: Then... you're one of us? You believe in the equal distribution of food regardless of species?

EditorData.NodeContext: Tentatively; believes the player might on their side

Text.Value: Are you not? Well, you aren't one of us.
We will! And we don't need your permission!
*Squeak!*
I'm not an oppressor!
Leave me be - I have siblings to forage for.
*Squeak.*
You lot hoard your delectable riches while my brothers and sisters starve!
Leave.
Exactly! And what good is displaying such morsels and not eating them? Food is for eating, friend!

EditorData.NodeContext: Passionately (and pleased the player is on their side)

Text.Value: We shall! We will fly in the face of the oppressors and their foolish laws! Leave no crust unnibbled!
Yes! Victuals for all! May you brux until your eyes boggle!

EditorData.NodeContext: Happy that the player is on their side; zealous celebration

Text.Value: I'm also here to do that, actually.
Sure. Now let's grab what we can and get out of here.
Then leave me to it.
Very well - discretion is the better part of valour.

EditorData.NodeContext: Annoyed but trying to leave with dignity
